snippet.title: "Having fun" in AMUSEMENT PARK - When ADRENALIN kicks in! Check out and LAUGH :)
snippet.description:
Amusement parks can be fun, but not for everyone. Some faint-hearted should just remain on the ground :D Here are examples of the best fails and reactions, mostly from babies, who didn't expect that level of adrenalin! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
